Package: python3-web3
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: python-keyfile-doc
Description: Utilities for working with Ethererum ABI definitions (Python 3)
 The web3 library provides low level utilities for converting python
 values to and from solidity's binary ABI format.
 .
 This package installs the library for Python 3.

